tool_description: Simple API, that allows you to get user's IP address.
title: IPInfoAPI

api_list.name: Generate IP
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://ipinfoapi.p.rapidapi.com/fakeip"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "ipinfoapi.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
